members.name: getPublicId
members.comment: The public identifier associated with the entity if specified, and null otherwise.

members.name: getSystemId
members.comment: The system identifier associated with the entity if specified, and null otherwise. This may be an absolute URI or not.

members.name: getNotationName
members.comment: For unparsed entities, the name of the notation for the entity. For parsed entities, this is null.

members.name: getInputEncoding
members.comment: An attribute specifying the encoding used for this entity at the time of parsing, when it is an external parsed entity. This is null if it an entity from the internal subset or if it is not known.

members.name: getXmlEncoding
members.comment: An attribute specifying, as part of the text declaration, the encoding of this entity, when it is an external parsed entity. This is null otherwise.

members.name: getXmlVersion
members.comment: An attribute specifying, as part of the text declaration, the version number of this entity, when it is an external parsed entity. This is null otherwise.
